      <div class="article-top">
                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden">Your muffin tin is for way more than muffins and cupcakes. Sweet or savory, these recipes hit the spot and can be eaten on the go.</div>
                <header class="article-header">
          <div class="group-article-meta">
            <div
  class="field field-name-post-date"
  itemprop="datePublished"
  content="2015-02-15"
>
  February 15, 2015  <span class="separator">|</span> </div>
            <div class="field article-author-top" itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
  <span class="label">By </span>
    <a
    href="http://greatist.com/p/nina-callaway"
    title="User profile of "
    class="username"
